All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AmazonCategoryPage
Page Object Class for the actions performed on Category Page in Amazon page
AmazonHamburgerMenuPage
Page Object Class for the actions performed on Hamburger Menu Page in Amazon Website
AmazonHomePage
Page Object Class for the actions performed on Home Page in Amazon Website
AmazonProductPage
Page Object Class for the actions performed on the Product page opened
AmazonTest
Test class containing all the tests related to the Amazon Coding Challenge
AmazonTestData
POJO class for Amazon Test Data JSON file
BaseTest
Parent class of all Test classes used for Setup and Tear down actions
BrowserInvocationFailureException
Custom Exception class capturing the issues with invocation of browser using DriverFactory
CategoryType
Custom Enum with the list of Category types to be added to Framework Annotation if used in any Test methods
ConfigProperties
Custom Enum with the values of all the properties defined in Config.properties file
DataProviderTest
Class containing all Data Providers to be applied for the Tests in Framework.
Driver
Class containing methods to initialize and quit Driver
DriverFactory
Factory class to implement browser invocation handling both remote and local runs
DriverManager
Class implementing Thread Safety mechanism for Driver Instances using ThreadLocal in case of parallel execution
DynamicXPathUtils
Utility class to generate Dynamic XPath values
ExplicitWaitFactory
Factory class to implement the Explicit wait with the input of which wait strategy has to be used
ExtentManager
Class implementing Thread Safety mechanism for writing the Extent Test details to Extent Report using ThreadLocal in case of parallel execution of Tests
ExtentReport
Class for instantiating Extent Report file and writing data of all the run tests details to the report.
FrameworkAnnotation
Custom Annotation created in the Framework Structure for adding Authors and Categories to Test Methods
FrameworkConfig
Interface for reading Config Properties file using Config Interface from Owner library
FrameworkConstants
Class with the list of Constant variables used in Automation Framework.
FrameworkException
Custom Exception class extending RuntimeException which signals that Framework related custom exceptions occurred
FrameworkLogger
Logger class using Consumer Interface feature of Java to log the status to Extent Test in Extent Report
ListenerClass
A Test listener class implementing the TestNG Listener ITestListener to listen to the Tests run by the Framework.
LogType
Custom Enum with the list of log types to be added to Framework Logger for logging any status
PageActions
Utility class to perform basic operations on WebElement such as Click, SendKeys efficiently
PropertyReader
Utility class to read Config.properties file using Config Interface from Owner library
ScreenshotUtils
Utility class to handle Screenshot operations in the Framework
WaitStrategy
Custom Enum with the list of Wait Strategies used for Explicit wait implementation for action on WebElements
WebElementNotFoundException
Custom Exception class capturing the issues with finding WebElement using ExplicitWaitFactory
